title: WHOREible Decisions LIVE!

description:
No episode this week as the ladies take a much needed break! It is our pleasure to announce we will be remaining on the Black Effect Network for another year!! Don't miss out on your chance to see your favorite podcast duo LIVE! 


Get your tickets NOW! WHOREible Decisions is back on the road! Get your tickets at Whorehive.com

Thursday 11/4 New York City

Friday 11/19 Washington, DC

Friday 12/3 Los Angeles

Friday 12/17 Atlanta


Follow the hosts on social media Weezy @Weezywtf & Mandii B @Fullcourtpumps and follow the Whoreible Decisions pages

Instagram @whoreible_decisions

Twitter @whoreiblepod


Don't forget to tag #whoreibledecisions or @ us to let us know what you think of this week's episode!

Want more? Bonus episodes, merch and more Whoreible Decisions!! Become a Patron at Patreon.com/whoreibledecisions


Want some Whoreible Decisions merchandise? GET YOURS NOW AT WHOREHIVE.COM
